# Puchi Frontend

Puchi là nền tảng web học tiếng Việt. Frontend dùng **Next.js 16 (App Router) + React 19**.

## Tech Stack

| Thành phần | Công nghệ |
|------------|-----------|
| Framework | Next.js 16 (App Router, output: standalone) |
| UI | Tailwind CSS v4 + Shadcn UI (New York) |
| State | Zustand v5 |
| Auth | Auth-service (self-hosted) — custom AuthProvider + fetch trực tiếp |
| i18n | next-intl (9 ngôn ngữ) |
| Animation | Motion + Rive |
| Runtime | Bun (install) + Node.js 22 (build & run) |

## Auth — Auth-service (self-hosted, xoá Zitadel)

**Đã migrate từ Zitadel → Auth-service tự xây dựng (Go/Kratos).** Flow:

### Custom AuthProvider
```typescript
// src/providers/AuthProvider.tsx
const auth = useAuth()
auth.login(email, password)    // POST /api/auth/login → set cookie + localStorage
auth.register(email, password) // POST /api/auth/register
auth.logout()                  // POST /api/auth/logout → clear state
```

### Auth flow tổng thể
```
Browser → custom form → api.puchi.io.vn/auth → auth-service:8080
       → Set-Cookie: refresh_token (HttpOnly, SameSite=None)
       → Response body: { access_token, expires_in, user }
```

### Endpoints (frontend gọi tới api.puchi.io.vn/auth/)

| Method | Path | Mô tả |
|--------|------|-------|
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Login |
| POST | `/api/auth/register` | Register |
| POST | `/api/auth/refresh` | Refresh token (cookie) |
| POST | `/api/auth/logout` | Logout (cookie) |
| GET | `/api/auth/social/{provider}` | OAuth2 redirect |
| POST | `/api/auth/magic-link/send` | Magic link (NATS → email) |
| PUT | `/api/auth/password/change` | Change password |
| GET | `/api/auth/sessions` | List sessions |
| DELETE | `/api/auth/sessions/{id}` | Revoke session |

## Docker Build

Multi-stage build với Bun + Node.js:

| Stage | Image | Purpose |
|-------|-------|---------|
| deps | `oven/bun:1.2-slim` | Install dependencies |
| builder | `node:22-alpine` | Build Next.js |
| runner | `node:22-alpine` | Run production (non-root user nextjs) |

Build args từ CI/CD:
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL` — https://puchi.io.vn
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` — https://api.puchi.io.vn

## CI/CD

GitHub Actions (`ci-cd.yml`):
- **Lint**: Bun install → ESLint
- **Build & Push**: Docker login GHCR → Build + Push (tag: latest + sha)
- **Build args**: NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_WEBSITE_DOMAIN
- **Registry**: `ghcr.io/puchidemy/puchi-frontend`

## Key Env Vars

| Env | Production value | Notes |
|-----|-----------------|-------|
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL` | `https://puchi.io.vn` | App domain |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` | `https://api.puchi.io.vn` | API gateway (dùng chung cho auth + backend) |

## Scripts

```bash
bun install          # Cài dependencies (dùng bun.lock)
bun run dev          # Dev server (webpack mode)
bun run build        # Build production (chạy bằng Node.js)
bun run start        # Start production
bun run lint         # ESLint
```

## Cấu trúc thư mục

```
src/
├── app/[locale]/         # Next.js App Router pages (i18n)
├── app/api/              # API routes (debug only — auth gọi thẳng api.puchi.io.vn)
├── components/           # UI components (Shadcn + custom)
│   └── auth/             # AuthCard, SignInForm, SignUpForm, SocialLoginButtons
├── actions/              # Server Actions (logout, etc.)
├── lib/                  # api-contracts.ts, backend.ts, client-api.ts
├── providers/            # AuthProvider (useAuth hook)
├── store/                # Zustand stores
├── hooks/                # Custom hooks
├── i18n/                 # Translation config
├── styles/               # Global styles
├── constants/            # Constants
├── config/               # env.ts (Zod-validated env config)
├── proxy.ts              # Middleware (xác thực bằng refresh_token cookie)
└── types/                # TypeScript types
```

## Kết nối Backend

- API: `api.puchi.io.vn` qua Envoy Gateway (dùng `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL`)
- Auth: gọi thẳng `api.puchi.io.vn/auth/*` (auth-service)
- Server-side fetch: đọc access_token từ cookie, gắn `Authorization: Bearer`
- Client-side fetch: `credentials: include` (cookie tự gửi theo domain)
